               <persName ref="#nathu">Nathu</persName>,
                son of Maqbul, acknowledges receipt of
               <measure type="currency" unit="rupee" quantity="13">13 rupees</measure>
                for the house he built on landlord (chaudhri)
               <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das's</persName>
                land.</p>
